    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW M\u2019s only production V8. At its heart is the S65 4.0L naturally aspirated engine, featuring eight individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system that pulls relentlessly to an 8,400 RPM redline. The power is managed via a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and the M Variable Differential Lock, providing exceptional mechanical grip. Recent service includes preventative rod bearing replacement and new throttle valve actuators, addressing the primary concerns of this high-performance platform. The chassis remains tight, equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) for adjustable compression and rebound settings. While the car shows minor aesthetic patina consistent with a well-loved driver, its structural integrity and drivetrain performance are robust. This is a purist-spec machine optimized for longitudinal and lateral G-loading.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
