    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2019 BMW X5 xDrive40i in Alpine White over a Canberra Beige Vernasca leather interior. This vehicle has been a reliable daily driver and is currently in solid, dependable condition. The exterior retains a deep, glossy shine, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front hood and a small 2-inch scuff on the rear passenger-side bumper\u2014typical for its age but worth noting for a discerning buyer. All four 19-inch V-spoke wheels are straight, though the front right wheel shows a light touch of curb rash. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of luxury. The leather is supple and free of tears, with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All technological features, including the iDrive 7.0 system, panoramic sunroof, and heated seats, function perfectly. Mechanically, this X5 is sound. It has a comprehensive service history with oil changes performed every 7,500 miles. The turbocharged inline-six engine pulls smoothly, and the 8-speed transmission shifts seamlessly. Recent maintenance includes a fresh brake fluid flush and a new cabin air filter. The tires currently have approximately 60% tread remaining, providing plenty of miles before needing replacement. This is a complete, honest car ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 34850.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
