    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride! It's been such a reliable companion and is still in really solid shape for its next owner. It\u2019s super clean, runs like a charm, and has plenty of life left in it. Perfect for someone who wants a dependable car without the brand-new price tag. Come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love how it drives!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
