      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced and the VANOS system has been overhauled to ensure long-term structural and timing integrity. The chassis maintains its signature balance through refreshed bushings and a well-sorted suspension geometry. While the exterior shows minor evidence of use, the powertrain delivers peak performance with a linear power band and crisp throttle response. A true driver's car that prioritizes mechanical excellence over showroom cosmetics.",
